{"tid":1020131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講英文係咪要收緊嘴唇？","createTime":"2019-02-13T11:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T15:40:26.000Z","uid":94388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab5454aa9625d69f6be8ae0f2a5ec97ade4eb3e","tid":1020131,"uid":94388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"英文發音比較陰柔（特別係英式），又分重弱音，弱音輕輕帶過就可以，感覺上「嘟」起個嘴會講得順同好聽D。<br />\n法文都好似係要收緊嘴唇黎講，比較浪漫。<br />\n相反，西班牙文同廣東話好似用嘴後半既肌肉多既，聽起來較粗獷豪邁。<br />\n有無語言專家可以講講，受教了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6215d5f841a4aba7c697ba02a0c84dd721546e08","tid":1020131,"uid":94388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f4f11c45c55a721d8fa340ae53d95137e20763","tid":1020131,"uid":140664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"法文既sound inventory入面<br />\nRounded vowel既數量較其他語言多同埋用射頻密<br />\n例如/y/ /&oslash;/ /&oelig;/<br />\n除左rounded vowel, back vowel同nasalised vowels都多(nasalised vowel 更係法文一個好重要既特徵）<br />\n所以聽落去會圓滑d<br />\n至於英式英文就.....冇咩研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf2a6bfbba53f34c042ce4959d0256c82fad67c","tid":1020131,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab5454aa9625d69f6be8ae0f2a5ec97ade4eb3e","tid":1020131,"uid":94388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"英文發音比較陰柔（特別係英式），又分重弱音，弱音輕輕帶過就可以，感覺上「嘟」起個嘴會講得順同好聽D。<br />\n法文都好似係要收緊嘴唇黎講，比較浪漫。<br />\n相反，西班牙文同廣東話好似用嘴後半既肌肉多既，聽起來較粗獷豪邁。<br />\n有無語言專家可以講講，受教了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face